section.journey
    .container
        div(class="wow animate__animated animate__fadeInUp" data-wow-delay="0.5s").title
            p Journey
            h2 Damien's Journey - A Timeline
        div(class="wow animate__animated animate__fadeInUp" data-wow-delay="0.5s").timeline__wrapper 
            .timeline__card 
                p Year - 2005
                span In 2005, Damien acquired her first camera, igniting her passion for photography. She started experimenting with landscapes and candid shots, marking the beginning of her visual storytelling journey.
            .timeline__card 
                p Year - 2010
                span Damien pursued a degree in Fine Arts with a focus on photography, refining her technical skills and artistic sensibilities.
            .timeline__card 
                p Year - 2012
                span In 2012, Damien held her first solo exhibition, showcasing her unique perspective on nature and people through her lens.
            .timeline__card 
                p Year - 2015
                span Damien officially launched her photography business in 2015, offering portrait, event, and commercial photography services.
            .timeline__card 
                p Year - 2017
                span Damien's work took her beyond the USA, capturing breathtaking scenes and cultures from around the world.
            .timeline__card 
                p Year - 2020
                span In 2020, Damien's dedication and creativity earned her several prestigious photography awards, solidifying her position as a visionary photographer.
        